mpmToolbox.projectData.alignment

Class Part

  • java.lang.Object
    • mpmToolbox.projectData.alignment.Part

  • public class Part
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of this is a Hashmap of all MSM notes, accessed via their XML ID. The notes are augmented with performance information.
    Author:
    Axel Berndt
